        <h2 class="section-title">The company-as-a-service platform &mdash; one founder, one AI organization, every department.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Not a copilot. Not an assistant. A full AI organization that reviews, plans, builds, remembers, and self-improves. Sam Altman has called the one-person billion-dollar company <a href="https://fortune.com/2024/02/04/sam-altman-one-person-unicorn-silicon-valley-founder-myth/" rel="noopener noreferrer">&ldquo;unimaginable without AI&rdquo; but something that &ldquo;now will happen.&rdquo;</a> Every decision you make teaches the system. Every feature or project gets better and faster than the last.</p>
